<h3>End notes:</h3> Make sure you check out <a target="_blank" href="http://www.javaserverfaces.org">www.javaserverfaces.org</a>. It's a great starting point and reference for JSF that you will undoubtably bookmark if doing a lot of work, and doing the work with this book. Also check out <a href="http://ocpsoft.com/prettyfaces/">http://ocpsoft.com/prettyfaces/</a> for more information on Pretty URLs in JSF, and building client-facing JSF web applications.
