As a vocal blogger, I feel responsible for promoting and sharing the good work of others, whether that be technology, creative work, or in this case: a book. I will take no exception to that philosophy when it comes to the <a target="_blank" href="http://www.javaserverfaces.org">JavaServer Faces</a> framework. For a quick read, try the summary. If you are intrigued, read on! I hope you find this review valuable.
